人员告知公安、消防人员处置结束、可以撤离，民警与消防在现场继续观察警戒和做好安监护，4 分钟后发生爆炸。 根据事故调查报告结果，其中 11 名事故责任人已被公安机关采取措施。 致 26 死、 138 伤！十堰重大燃气爆炸事故调查报告全文首次公布"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-ad02a29b7a11ef083da210ed25608d7a_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "221 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/490228405"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIvf7Lzf/O04R5EAMaCDcxMjIxMDA1IPP03ooGMCQ42ghAC3IJNDkwMjI4NDA1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1633154564.4818842", "card_id": "Q_490069436", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 51}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待美国财政部长耶伦呼吁取消联邦政府债务上限?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "当地时间 9 月 30 日，美国财政部长耶伦在众议院金融服务委员会听证会上表示，她支持取消联邦债务上限，并称其对美国人信心及美国信用产生「极具破坏性」的威胁。 耶伦表示，对财政部发行的债券规模任意设置上限会限制该部门承担国会和总统已经批准的法案的能力，是没有意义的。耶伦强调，若要为支出和税收法案提供资金，就必须发行额外债券，若财政部无法支付这些债务，则将产生破坏性的后果。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picb.zhimg.com/50/v2-2b381d7e189d1eaa9f548da5ecd47764_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "220 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/490069436"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ivf7Lzf/O04R5EAMaCDcxMTg1NTg2IMec2IoGMAg4jAJADHIJNDkwMDY5NDM2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1633154564.4823534", "card_id": "Q_489081507", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 76}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "一个人的外貌很重要吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-2aea5ab8e870a0beda36fe2dc9fa07cf_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "209 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/489081507"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ivf7Lzf/O04R5EAMaCDcwOTY2MzQ5IMC5v4oGMAI4jwFADXIJNDg5MDgxNTA3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=