张某琴、胡某和张某熹等 8 名男生在校内饭店吃饭饮酒，期间以上三人醉酒。因深夜女生宿舍关闭，2 名女生被同行人员送至张某熹宿舍醒酒，后被辅导员及保卫处工作人员及时发现，遂送至学院保卫处醒酒。该过程被围观学生黄某用自己手机拍摄并发至微信群，同时出于好玩心理，黄在群中捏造了「这些人在发生性关系」之类的文字，导致该事件网传发酵。 目前，在校学生黄某（未满 18 周岁）因编造虚假信息引发网络舆情，我局已对其给予批评教育处理，并责令监护人严加管教。（昌南公安） 【江西科技职业学院回应「两女生被拖进男宿舍」：不实，已报警】 9 月 27 日，网传江西某高校两女生喝醉后被拖进男生宿舍。9 月 28 日，江西科技职业学院回应称：网传「江西科技职业学院女生被拉进男生宿舍强奸」为不实消息，校方已报警。（七环视频）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-188c236873a48550b5d34bf48b57b461_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "30 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/489676822"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ivf7Lzf/O04R5EAMaCDcxMDk4NDQ5IO3+zooGMEU4igtAL3IJNDg5Njc2ODIyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1633154564.4971147", "card_id": "Q_488628729", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么 ProMotion 在 iPad Pro 上使用要比 iPhone 13 Pro 更耗电?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-dcbf167921a62a09cef43fd10fa6f690_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "30 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/488628729"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ivf7Lzf/O04R5EAMaCDcwODY1NzY2INq9s4oGMAI4QEAwcgk0ODg2Mjg3Mjl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1633154564.4974291", "card_id": "Q_481711175", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 3224}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "初一初二根本什么都没学，初三开学努力还来得及吗?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我初一初二啥也不会哇"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-a46727ce55588674584ee2e81006c29c_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "30 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/481711175"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ivf7L